msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn40.10:52.2"
msgid "‘svākkhāto bhagavatā dhammo … pe … paccattaṃ veditabbo viññūhī’ti. "
msgstr " "

msgctxt "sn40.10:52.3"
msgid "Dhamme aveccappasādena samannāgamanahetu kho, mārisa moggallāna, evam’idhekacce sattā kāyassa bhedā paraṃ maraṇā sugatiṃ saggaṃ lokaṃ upapajjanti. "
